<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10259398>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Agyneta hum n. sp. Male. A, palp, retrolateral view. B, palp, prolateral view. C, embolus, prolateral view. D, radical division, retrolateral view. E, palp tibia, dorsal view. F, cymbium, mesodorsal view. G–H, male habitus. Scale bars (A–F): 0.2 mm, (G–H): 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10259398/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10259400>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Agyneta hum n. sp. Female. A, epigynum, ventral view. B, internal genitalia, ventral view. C, internal genitalia, dorsal view. D, internal genitalia, lateral view. E–F, female habitus. Scale bars (A–D): 0.2 mm, (E–F): 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10259400/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10259408>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Agyneta hum n. sp. Male, SEM images.A, chelicerae. B, pedipalp (retrolateral view). C, pedipalp (prolateral view). D, detail of the lamella characteristica. E, dorsal and ventral tubercles (enclosed box of Fig. 5C). Scale bars (A–C): 0.1 mm, (D–E): 0.05 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10259408/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10259414>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Agyneta hum n. sp. (A, B) and Agyneta unguiserrata n. sp. (C, D) Females, SEM images. A and C, chelicerae. B and D, epigynum. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10259414/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10259416>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. A, Map distribution of Agyneta hum n. sp. (black circles) and Agyneta unguiserrata n. sp. (white squares). B, riparian native forest (Arévalo, Cerro Largo, Uruguay), A. hum n. sp. preferred habitat. C, grassland (near La Paloma city, Durazno, Uruguay), A. unguiserrata n. sp. habitat in Uruguay." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10259416/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

